{
  "stem": "20405.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because this Baron he helped so much for this neighborhood and for the Jewish people, they give the name that neighborhood Baron Hirsch.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, like any other synagogue, very beautiful synagogue with [INAUDIBLE] at the end of that and with a chair.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it really was a beautiful synagogue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Sephardic only.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandparents, they send me the Italian consulate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because my mother was with five kids.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she didn't have the-- the-- she didn't have the-- the way how to support us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Italian consulate, which they help us very-- too much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not only us, to many Jewish people I can tell you that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After when-- even when the Germans was in Thessaloniki, the Italian consulate was giving some false certificates to get them out from the ghetto, which it happened to many people that I know.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they sent me to Italy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They proposed to my mother to send me to Italy to study over there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I was the oldest of the family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she couldn't afford to feed us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 13.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went right to Milan to a private college, Milan, which I didn't have to pay nothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were with about 300 people, 300 [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] young people with a church in it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was the only Jewish at the church.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I was a little behind from my class.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they priest every night, he would take me to his office to give me some lessons to be able to be in the same level with the other students.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I don't think this was a reason to help me out.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
